@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Create message
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "conversationId": 1,
  "text": "Hello Sara, this is my first message."
}

### List messages for conversation 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages?conversationId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
